testTools_OAuthSample and testTools_OAuthSampleWeb

These 2 projects are the test application used for testing MessageSight OAuth support with WebSphere Application Server.

To create the application, right click testTools_OAuthSample and export as an ear file.
Install the application into WAS. After installing, click the application name to enter its configuration page.
Click on "Security role to user/group mapping" and check the box for "All Role" and click "Map Users..."

Click "Search", select all user entries that appear and click the right arrow to move them to the "Selected" panel.
Click OK, click OK, click Save.
Start the application.

The URL for the application will be https://[WAS_SERVER_IP]:[https_port]/MessageSightOAuth